title: Part A
stimulusHtml:
Select a point value to view scoring criteria, solutions, and/or examples to score the response.

The first point does not require a simplified answer. Substitution of function values is required.

The second point requires a time reference, a rate, and units. The point may be earned with an incorrect approximation based on one computational error and provided the behavior described is consistent with the sign of the approximation, the numerical value, and the time reference.
